  <div class="teaser-date">06/23/25</div>
  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/ever-changing-universe-revealed-in-first-imagery-from-nsf-doe-vera-c-rubin-observatory?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span>Ever-changing universe revealed in first imagery from NSF-DOE Vera C. Rubin Observatory</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>The world’s largest digital camera brings the night sky to life like never before.</p>

